<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:28:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>消息人士称，法国、希腊、意大利、波兰将支持中国电动汽车关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/france-greece-italy-poland-set-back-chinese-ev-tariffs-sources-say-2024-10-02/</link><description>法国、希腊、意大利和波兰将于周五投票支持对中国制造的电动汽车(EV)进口征收高达45%的关税，足以让欧盟提案获得通过，此举可能会加剧贸易紧张局势消息人士称，与北京的合作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/france-greece-italy-poland-set-back-chinese-ev-tariffs-sources-say-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>德国肖尔茨呼吁与中国就电动汽车进行更多谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germanys-scholz-talks-with-china-electric-vehicles-must-continue-2024-10-02/</link><description>德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨周三表示，排除外国竞争并缩小贸易伙伴范围的做法是错误的，并表示必须继续与中国就电动汽车进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 11:30:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germanys-scholz-talks-with-china-electric-vehicles-must-continue-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟要求 YouTube、Snapchat、TikTok 提供有关内容算法的信息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-requests-information-youtube-snapchat-tiktok-about-recommendations-2024-10-02/</link><description>周三，欧盟委员会要求 YouTube、Snapchat 和 TikTok 提供信息，了解其算法向用户推荐内容所使用的参数，以及它们在放大一些系统性风险（包括与选举过程、心理健康和未成年人保护相关的风险）方面所扮演的角色。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:14:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-requests-information-youtube-snapchat-tiktok-about-recommendations-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中东紧张局势、港口罢工导致第四季度开局紧张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-02/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>2025年钻石联赛揭幕战两项赛事将在中国举办，决赛将在苏黎世举行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/china-host-opening-two-events-2025-diamond-league-final-zurich-2024-10-02/</link><description>组织者周三表示，苏黎世将于 8 月举行为期两天的 2025 年钻石联赛赛季决赛，比赛将在中国举行两场比赛。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 09:14:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/china-host-opening-two-events-2025-diamond-league-final-zurich-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，200多名中国公民从黎巴嫩撤离</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/more-than-200-chinese-citizens-evacuated-lebanon-state-media-says-2024-10-02/</link><description>据中国官方新华社周三报道，黎巴嫩政府已安全撤离200多名中国公民。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 08:54:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/more-than-200-chinese-citizens-evacuated-lebanon-state-media-says-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>即将离任的戴姆勒卡车首席执行官认为中国和德国没有复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/outgoing-daimler-truck-ceo-sees-no-recovery-china-germany-2024-10-02/</link><description>全球最大卡车制造商戴姆勒卡车即将卸任的首席执行官马丁·道姆 (Martin Daum) 在周二晚间的新闻发布会上表示，中国和德国卡车市场的复苏不会很快到来。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 08:48:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/outgoing-daimler-truck-ceo-sees-no-recovery-china-germany-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>官员称，通过台湾海峡的德国船只已被警告驶离</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/german-ships-that-passed-through-taiwan-strait-were-warned-off-officials-say-2024-10-02/</link><description>德国特遣小组指挥官周三表示，上个月穿越台湾海峡的德国海军舰艇受到了中国船只的密切监视和重复无线电信息，但没有出现不安全行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 07:56:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/german-ships-that-passed-through-taiwan-strait-were-warned-off-officials-say-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>南海紧张局势下，菲律宾吸引国防公司进行军事现代化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/philippines-draws-defence-firms-military-modernises-amid-south-china-sea-tension-2024-10-02/</link><description>在南海紧张局势加剧之际，菲律宾正在投入数十亿美元进行军队现代化的最新阶段，全球国防承包商展示了他们的先进硬件。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 07:53:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/philippines-draws-defence-firms-military-modernises-amid-south-china-sea-tension-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>IEA表示，氢能项目投资正在加速，但不确定性仍然存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/hydrogen-project-investments-are-accelerating-uncertainty-remains-iea-says-2024-10-02/</link><description>国际能源署 (IEA) 在周三的一份报告中表示，过去 12 个月，氢项目的最终投资决定增加了一倍，其中以中国为主，但由于该行业面临不确定性，装机容量和需求较低。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 05:06:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/hydrogen-project-investments-are-accelerating-uncertainty-remains-iea-says-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警首次进入北极与俄罗斯联合巡逻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-coast-guard-enters-arctic-first-time-patrol-with-russia-2024-10-02/</link><description>据官方媒体周三报道，中国海警船队首次进入北冰洋，与俄罗斯海警船队进行联合巡逻。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 04:46:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-coast-guard-enters-arctic-first-time-patrol-with-russia-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>随着焦点转向美国经济数据，黄金涨势暂停</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-prices-flat-dollar-strength-counters-safe-haven-demand-2024-10-02/</link><description>周三金价走软，在上一交易日因中东冲突升级而上涨后稍作喘息，而交易员则等待有关美国利率的更多线索。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 04:02:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-prices-flat-dollar-strength-counters-safe-haven-demand-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>由于谨慎的投资者关注中东的敌对行动，股市稳定，油价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-02/</link><description>周三股市坚挺，政府债券和美元等避险资产上涨，因为中东敌对行动不断升级，投资者抑制了恐慌性抛售，油价也上涨了近 3%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 01:30:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>台湾因台风“Krathon”停工，带来暴雨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-shuts-down-ahead-typhoon-krathons-arrival-torrential-rain-forecast-2024-10-02/</link><description>台湾周三关闭，数百架航班停飞，学校、办公室和金融市场关闭，随后台风“克拉松”即将到来，据报道造成一人死亡，台湾南部遭遇暴雨。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 00:45:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-shuts-down-ahead-typhoon-krathons-arrival-torrential-rain-forecast-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国财政部官员称国际货币基金组织对中国政策和融资保证“过于礼貌”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/imf-too-polite-china-policies-financing-assurances-us-treasury-official-says-2024-10-01/</link><description>美国财政部一位高级官员周二表示，国际货币基金组织在批评中国经济政策时“过于客气”，应更全面地披露中国和其他一些国家为支持国际货币基金组织贷款计划而提供的融资保证。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 22:32:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/imf-too-polite-china-policies-financing-assurances-us-treasury-official-says-2024-10-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>